@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rpyqcb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.05 / v1 + 0.71) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.56)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.39) - 0.52) * (wp.cos(v0 + 0.98) * (tmp + 0.45 * v2 + 0.95)))
    data[tid] = v0
